        <title>the-1st-post</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi people, I choose &lt;a href=&quot;http://octopress.org/&quot;&gt;Octopress 3&lt;/a&gt; and theme it with &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/itsrifat/rifyll&quot;&gt;rifyll&lt;/a&gt; as my personal cat-style blog. This &lt;code&gt;blogging framework for hacker&lt;/code&gt; cool known for programmers blog about their ideas. Octopress features - &lt;!--- [(more)](/blog/2015/05/24/the-1st-post.html) --&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Pygments syntax highlighting &amp;amp; Markdown based posts&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Out of the box support for publishing straight to GitHub pages&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Built in support for third-party services like Google Analytics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Installation steps:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 1&lt;/code&gt; Install Jekyll and Octopress 3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# Installing Octopress 3 automatically installs Jekyll as a dependency.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;gem install octopress&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 2&lt;/code&gt; Download &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/itsrifat/rifyll&quot;&gt;Rifyll&lt;/a&gt; themed Octopress blog scaffold.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 3&lt;/code&gt; Cd to Rifyll directory &amp;amp; New a post&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# This generates a new post yyyy-mm-dd-title.markdown under `_post`.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nb&quot;&gt;cd &lt;/span&gt;rifyll-master
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;octopress new post &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;title&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 4&lt;/code&gt; Build _site&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# This builds a blog site dir under `_site`.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;jekyll build&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;(optional)&lt;/code&gt; &lt;code&gt;step 5&lt;/code&gt; Preview locally (&lt;strong&gt;NOTE&lt;/strong&gt; before deployment please kill this process)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# This runs a server up at port 4000.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# Server address: http://127.0.0.1:4000/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;jekyll serve &lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 6&lt;/code&gt; Set up deployment of website to GitHub&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# setup method of deployment to github&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;octopress deploy init git --url git@github.com:NAME/NAME.github.io.git&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;step 7&lt;/code&gt; Deploy the built website&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bash&quot; data-lang=&quot;bash&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;c&quot;&gt;# deploy built site&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;lineno&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;$ &lt;/span&gt;octopress deploy&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;finish step&lt;/code&gt; Youâ€™d see this. Done.&lt;/p&gt;

